}}'''''BraveStarr''''' is a 1987 [[action game]] developed by [[Probe Software]] and published under [[U.S. Gold]]'s Go! label. Based on the [[BraveStarr|animated series and toyline of the same name]], the player assumes the role of Marshal BraveStarr.

The game received generally negative reviews from video game critics.

